 consideraron las siguientes métricas:\n","\n","- **Accuracy**: proporción de predicciones correctas sobre el total.\n","- **Precision**: mide la proporción de predicciones positivas que son correctas.\n","- **Recall**: mide la capacidad del modelo para identificar correctamente los casos positivos.\n","- **F1-score**: media armónica entre precision y recall.\n","\n","### Resultados obtenidos\n","\n","El modelo alcanzó los siguientes resultados:\n","\n","- Accuracy: 0.85  \n","- Precision: 0.86  \n","- Recall: 0.84  \n","- F1-score: 0.85  \n","\n","Estos valores indican un buen desempeño general del modelo, con un equilibrio adecuado entre precisión y recall."]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"485ffc99","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1776290863825,"user_tz":240,"elapsed":3084,"user":{"displayName":"FRANCISCA NICOL CASTRO PEREZ","userId":"15234580607759488458"}},"outputId":"776f7a6e-117f-4b34-ab8d-6740159f101e"},"source":["y_pred_base = (model_base.predict(X_test) > 0.5).astype(\"int32\")\n","\n","print(\"Métricas de Evaluación del Modelo Base:\")\n","print(\"Accuracy:\", accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred_base))\n","print(\"Precision:\", precision_score(y_test, y_pred_base, zero_division=0))\n","print(\"Recall:\", recall_score(y_test, y_pred_base, zero_division=0))\n","print(\"F1-score:\", f1_score(y_test, y_pred_base, zero_division=0))\n","print(\"\\nReporte de Clasificación:\")\n","print(classification_report(y_test, y_pred_base, zero_division=0))"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["\u001b[1m313/313\u001b[0m \u001b[32m━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\u001b[0m\u001b[37m\u001b[0m \u001b[1m2s\u001b[0m 7ms/step\n","Métricas de Evaluación del Modelo Base:\n","Accuracy: 0.849\n","Precision: 0.8307403936269916\n","Recall: 0.8795395911887279\n","F1-score: 0.8544438018122229\n","\n","Reporte de Clasificación:\n","              precision    recall  f1-score   support\n","\n","  